<h2 id="turkiyede-unesco-dunya-mirasi-alanlari-bir-kesif-rehberi" class="wp-block-heading">UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Turkey: A Discovery Guide</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey has a rich cultural heritage with 18 UNESCO World Heritage Sites. These sites offer visitors unique experiences with both their historical and natural beauty. Here are some of the key UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Turkey:</p>
<div id="model-response-message-contentr_7dc0e9532bb0e1b5" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" dir="ltr">
<h3>Turkey’s UNESCO World Heritage Sites</h3>
<p>Turkey&#8217;s entries on the UNESCO World Heritage List are categorized under two main headings: cultural and mixed (natural and cultural) heritage.</p>
<h3>1. Mixed Heritage Sites</h3>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<td>Site</td>
