<tbody>
<tr>
<td><b>Göreme National Park and the Rock Sites of Cappadocia</b></td>
<td>Nevşehir</td>
<td>1985</td>
<td>A unique natural landscape with fairy chimneys, cave churches, and underground settlements, featuring Christian architecture from the Byzantine period.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Hierapolis-Pamukkale</b></td>
<td>Denizli</td>
<td>1988</td>
<td>The natural beauty of travertine terraces combined with the ruins of the Roman-era thermal city of Hierapolis.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h3>2. Cultural Heritage Sites</h3>
