<td>İzmir</td>
<td>2015</td>
<td>An important port city of the Hellenistic and Roman periods, which also housed the Temple of Artemis, one of the Seven Wonders of the Ancient World.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Archaeological Site of Ani</b></td>
<td>Kars</td>
<td>2016</td>
