<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey is a country that offers international students opportunities for education, cultural experiences, and an affordable lifestyle. The richness of its UNESCO World Heritage Sites provides significant contributions to students&#8217; academic and personal development. For young people wishing to study, Turkey promises a rich experience both academically and socially. If you are considering studying in Turkey, we recommend you don&#8217;t miss out on these opportunities.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-18T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:51:11Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'a-guide-to-turkeys-unesco-world-heritage-sites' );
