<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In big cities (Istanbul, Ankara, Izmir, etc.) it usually ranges between 500 – 800 USD. In small cities and towns, the average is around 350 – 550 USD.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-where-to-find-special-discounts-for-students">5. Where to find special discounts for students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Special discounts for students are offered in some stores, online platforms and at events organized by universities.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-09-23T07:57:40Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T19:19:39Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/affordable-home-furnishings-shopping-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Affordable home furniture and decor shopping in Turkey","title":"affordable-home-furnishings-shopping-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'affordable-home-goods-shopping-in-turkey' );
