:"en-US","width":"450","height":"445"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo"}},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping/","name":"Shopping Mall Culture in Turkey and the Importance of Modern Shopping - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2026-04-15T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-04-15T14:00:00+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Shopping Mall Culture in Turkey and the Importance of Modern Shopping - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2026-04-15T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-04-15T14:00:00+03:00","articleSection":"Student Life and Travel","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Discover the shopping mall culture in Turkey and the impact of modern retail. Read now to enrich your shopping experience as an international student!","name":"Shopping Mall Culture in Turkey and the Importance of Modern Shopping - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Shopping malls (AVMs) have become a significant cultural phenomenon in Turkey in recent years. These venues, which attract both local and foreign visitors, are preferred not only for shopping but also for social interaction and entertainment. In this article, we will discuss the shopping mall culture in Turkey, the history of these centers, their popularity, and the experiences they offer.</p>
<h2 id="turkiyede-avm-kulturu-bir-alisveris-deneyimi" class="wp-block-heading">Shopping Mall Culture in Turkey: A Shopping Experience</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, shopping malls have fundamentally changed the shopping experience. With their modern architecture, a wide range of stores, restaurants, cinemas, and entertainment areas, malls serve not just as places to shop but also as social meeting points. Especially in large cities, shopping centers attract the interest of both locals and tourists.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The experience offered in malls goes beyond shopping, presenting visitors with a lifestyle. For example, many malls bring visitors together with organized events and festivals, while also creating a family-friendly environment by offering playgrounds for children and relaxation areas for adults.</p>
<h2 id="turkiyenin-ilk-avmsi-hangisi" class="wp-block-heading">What Was Turkey&#8217;s First Shopping Mall?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey&#8217;s first shopping mall was &#8220;Galleria,&#8221; which opened in 1988. Located in Istanbul&#8217;s Bakırköy district, this mall broke new ground in both shopping and entertainment. As the first example of a shopping mall in Turkey, Galleria stood out with both its architecture and the facilities it offered.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">With the opening of Galleria, mall culture in Turkey began to develop rapidly, and many new shopping centers were built. Over time, these centers started offering larger and more diverse services.</p>
<h2 id="yurt-disindan-gelen-ogrenciler-icin-turkiyede-avm-ziyareti-ipuclari" class="wp-block-heading">Tips for International Students Visiting Malls in Turkey</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For international students, malls in Turkey offer opportunities for both shopping and social interaction. Here are some tips to make this experience more enjoyable:</p>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Use Student Discounts:</strong> Many malls offer special discounts for students. You can take advantage of these <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkcede-alisveris-pazarlik-kaliplari/">discounts</a> by showing your student ID.</li>
<li><strong>Follow the Events:</strong> Malls frequently organize concerts, exhibitions, and other events. By participating in these activities, you can both have fun and meet new people.</li>
<li><strong>Try Local Flavors:</strong> You can try various delicacies from Turkish cuisine in the mall restaurants. Tasting local dishes like kebab, döner, and pide will enrich your cultural experience in Turkey.</li>
<li><strong>Plan Your Shopping:</strong> While spending time in malls is fun, it&#8217;s helpful to set a budget when <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-yerel-pazarlar/">shopping</a>. This can help you avoid unnecessary expenses.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="turkiyedeki-en-populer-alisveris-merkezleri-ve-nedenleri" class="wp-block-heading">The Most Popular Shopping Malls in Turkey and Why</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Among the most popular shopping malls in Turkey are the following:</p>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Cevahir Shopping Mall (Istanbul):</strong> Holding the distinction of being one of Europe&#8217;s largest shopping malls, Cevahir stands out with its extensive range of stores and entertainment areas.</li>
<li><strong>Mall of Istanbul:</strong> Known for its modern architecture and diverse brands, Mall of Istanbul is an ideal place for both shopping and entertainment.</li>
<li><strong>Forum Istanbul:</strong> It offers visitors an unforgettable experience with its aquarium, amusement park, and numerous stores.</li>
<li><strong>Ankara Panora:</strong> As the largest shopping mall in the capital city of Ankara, Panora is a popular spot for both shopping and social events.</li>
</ul>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These shopping malls attract the interest of both local and international visitors with their wide product ranges, entertainment options, and social spaces.</p>
<h2 id="avmlerde-kulturel-deneyimler-yeme-icme-ve-eglence-alternatifleri" class="wp-block-heading">Cultural Experiences in Malls: Food, Drink, and Entertainment Alternatives</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Malls are not just for shopping; they are also places that offer cultural experiences. The food, drink, and entertainment alternatives in Turkish malls are quite diverse:</p>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Food Courts:</strong> Malls feature restaurants offering flavors from many different cuisines. Besides Turkish cuisine, it is possible to find options from world cuisines.</li>
<li><strong>Cinema and Entertainment Areas:</strong> Malls have entertainment options such as movie theaters, bowling alleys, and arcades. These areas allow you to have a pleasant time with both friends and family.</li>
<li><strong>Event Spaces:</strong> Some malls host events like art exhibitions, concerts, and festivals. These events offer visitors a cultural experience.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="turkiyenin-en-buyuk-avmsi-neresi" class="wp-block-heading">Where is the Biggest Shopping Mall in Turkey?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey&#8217;s largest shopping mall is &#8220;Mall of Istanbul,&#8221; located in Istanbul. Opened in 2014, this giant shopping center is equipped with over 350 stores, movie theaters, entertainment areas, and restaurants. Mall of Istanbul serves not only as a place for shopping but also as a social living space.</p>
<h2 id="sik-sorulan-sorular-faq" class="wp-block-heading">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What brands can be found in Turkish malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkish malls, you can find many world-renowned brands. A wide range of products is offered, from clothing and electronics to home goods and cosmetics.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What are the food options in the malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to local Turkish cuisine, malls offer many different options such as Italian, Mexican, Asian, and fast food.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Which is the most popular mall in Turkey?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cevahir Shopping Mall is one of the most popular shopping centers in Turkey and stands out with its wide range of stores.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What activities are there for children in the malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Malls have many activities for children, such as playgrounds, movie theaters, and amusement parks. These areas allow families to have an enjoyable time with their children.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What should I pay attention to when shopping in malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When shopping, it is important to set a budget, look for discounts, and plan your needs in advance. Additionally, you can have a social experience by following the events in the malls.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-04-15T11:00:00Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-16T19:51:04Z' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping';
