<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkish malls, you can find many world-renowned brands. A wide range of products is offered, from clothing and electronics to home goods and cosmetics.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What are the food options in the malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to local Turkish cuisine, malls offer many different options such as Italian, Mexican, Asian, and fast food.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Which is the most popular mall in Turkey?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cevahir Shopping Mall is one of the most popular shopping centers in Turkey and stands out with its wide range of stores.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What activities are there for children in the malls?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Malls have many activities for children, such as playgrounds, movie theaters, and amusement parks. These areas allow families to have an enjoyable time with their children.</p>
