<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When shopping, it is important to set a budget, look for discounts, and plan your needs in advance. Additionally, you can have a social experience by following the events in the malls.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-15T11:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:51:04Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'shopping-mall-culture-in-turkey-and-the-importance-of-modern-shopping' );
