<li><b>Places to Visit:</b> The famous large breakfast halls that come to mind when you think of a &#8220;Van Breakfast,&#8221; and places offering local products.</li>
</ul>
<p><b>2. Trabzon / Black Sea Region (Mıhlama and Natural Products)</b></p>
