<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Apa saja tips praktis untuk sarapan?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Memilih tempat lokal, menggunakan produk segar, dan terbuka terhadap keragaman akan memperkaya pengalaman sarapan Anda.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-02-28T07:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-06T10:13:18Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'id' AND "slug" = 'budaya-dan-tempat-sarapan-di-turki' );
