<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What dishes are typically prepared during bayram in Turkey?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">During the bayrams, dishes such as baklava, kebab, *yaprak sarması* (stuffed grape leaves), *pide*, and various desserts are generally prepared. Each region has its own unique flavors.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-04-13T07:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:50:58Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'bayram-holidays-in-turkey-activities-and-recommendations' );
